"   <h1>",
"    REFERENCES",
"   </h1>",
"   <ol id=\"reference\">",
"    <li>",
"     Recht M, Pearson H. The hemolytic anemias. In: Oski's Pediatrics, McMillan JA, Deangelis CD, Feigin RD, Warshaw JB (Eds), Lippincott Williams and Wilkins, Philadelphia 1999. p.1453.",
